text:
Hi!
You need to change the `width: auto` to `width: 100%`  here:

```@media (max-width: 767px)
layout.min.css:1
.row-fluid [class*="span"] {
    display: block;
    float: none;
    width: auto; &lt;----
    margin-left: 0;
}```

Correct css below:

```@media (max-width: 767px)
layout.min.css:1
.row-fluid [class*="span"] {
    display: block;
    float: none;
    width: 100%;
    margin-left: 0;
}```
